### GitHub MCP Example API
### Make sure Compozy is running on localhost:5001 and MCP gateway is available.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v0
@workflowId = github_mcp

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Execute workflow to fetch latest PR for a repository
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# @name executeWorkflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}/executions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": {
    "repository": "compozy/compozy"
  }
}

### Extract execution ID
@execId = {{executeWorkflow.response.body.data.exec_id}}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Get execution details
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/executions/workflows/{{execId}}
Accept: application/json
